{"tid":1973270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疑政見不同遭包圍　強吻男子求突圍　67歲婦被控非禮襲擊　押後與控方商討","createTime":"2020-04-15T05:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T06:01:33.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"476482fcbfdc37c2595cbbd3b47815ea8c39512b","tid":1973270,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n六旬婦去年9月疑因政見不同，與一對年輕男女在公園內起爭執，期間遭男子及其他人士包圍，無法離開。婦人無計可施下，強吻了男子嘴唇一下，雙方及後發生肢體衝突。婦人被控非禮及普通襲擊共3罪，今日在西九龍裁判法院再應訊，辯方申請押後，以待與控方商討用其他方式處理，案件押後至5月27日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今日申請毋須答辯，要求押後案件，以待辯方索取法律意見，以及與控方商討以其他方式處理案件。被告獲准以原有條件繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n被告吳葉淑芬（67歲，退休人士），被控一項非禮及兩項普通襲擊罪，控罪指她於2019年9月5日在長沙灣海麗邨海和樓公園，猥褻侵犯並兩次襲擊男子X。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC4664/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0a7c650c-dd70-4fe7-a6b4-57d3778668f1_S0gso_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F0a7c650c-dd70-4fe7-a6b4-57d3778668f1_S0gso_1200x0.png&h=c65bcb07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/疑政見不同遭包圍-強吻男子求突圍-67歲婦被控非禮襲擊-押後與控方商討/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%BB%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%B1%82%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D-67%E6%AD%B2%E5%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%88%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E5%95%86%E8%A8%8E%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQPjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=a231be12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%96%91%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E9%81%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D-%E5%BC%B7%E5%90%BB%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%B1%82%E7%AA%81%E5%9C%8D-67%E6%AD%B2%E5%A9%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E6%8A%BC%E5%BE%8C%E8%88%87